reviewText: Great video for those interested in the Titanic.
Very well done movie.  I enjoy anything about the doomed ship.  This was done well. I recommend it to anyone.
Interesting story and well worth watching.  A small ton in Ireland that loses 16% of its population on the Titanic.
The Dvd was interesting  and the order came earlier than I expected can't get enough of Titanic History will be ordering more.
My husband has always enjoyed material about the Titanic. This DVD looked very interesting and different from the ones I've seen before.
